<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
<title>단기운전자 확대 특약 신청</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/directH1.css">
<script src="../../js/jquery/jquery-1.8.3.min.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/ui.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/ui_common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="popWrap">
		<header>
			<h1>단기운전자 확대 특약 신청</h1>
		</header>
		<div class="popContent">
			<p class="topTxt">기간은 최소 1일 ~ 최대 60일까지 입니다.</p>
			<section>
				<h2>보험기간</h2>
				<fieldset>
					<legend>단기운전자 확대 특약 신청</legend>					
					<div class="inputWrap ">
						<input type="text" id="carTermStart" required />
						<label for="carTermStart">시작일을 입력해 주세요(20170101)</label>
					</div>
					<div class="inputWrap ">
						<input type="text" id="carTermStart" required />
						<label for="carTermStart">종료일을 입력해 주세요(20170101)</label>
					</div>
				<fieldset>
				<ul class="listDot">
					<li>보험기간은 게시일로부터 <span class="fontOrg">7일</span>간입니다.</li>
				</ul>
				<div class="btnWrap">
					<span><a href="#" role="button">이전</a></span>
					<span class="on"><a href="#" role="button">다음</a></span>
			</div>
			</section>
		</div>
		<button type="button" class="btnClose" onclick="window.close();">창닫기</button>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
